Package: ctgov
Title: State of Connecticut Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Connecticut Socrata Open Data portal (data.ct.gov).
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for mill rates, corrections,
    licenses, and 629+ state datasets.
